Artur's build of the suckless Dynamic Window Manager [dwm-6.2]
--------------------------------------------------------------
dwm is a dynamic window manager for X made by suckless.org

The following patches were applied:
	1. dwm-autostart: Allows to run startup applications on dwm start.
		https://dwm.suckless.org/patches/autostart/
	2. dwm-bar-height: Adjustable top bar height.
		https://dwm.suckless.org/patches/bar_height/
	3. dwm-fullgaps: Add gaps between client windows.
		https://dwm.suckless.org/patches/fullgaps/
	4. dwm-hide_vacant_tags: This patch prevents dwm from drawing tags with no clients.
		https://dwm.suckless.org/patches/hide_vacant_tags/
	5. dwm-statuscmd: This patch adds the ability to execute shell commands based on the mouse button and position when clicking the status bar.
		https://dwm.suckless.org/patches/statuscmd/
	6. dwm-xrdb: Allows dwm to read colors from xrdb.
		https://dwm.suckless.org/patches/xrdb/
	7. dwm-centeredmaster: Added two stack layouts to dwm.

Some of the patches were slightly altered in order to play nice with my system configuration.

Additional features:
	* Removed iscol function inside drw.c in order to handle color icons/emojis in the statusbar.
	* Tweaked minor appearance settings.

Keyboard shortcuts:
	Super+r - run command via dmenu
	Super+Shift+Enter - open new terminal window
	Super+b - toggle bar
	Super+i - increase master
	Super+d - decrease master
	Super+j - focus previous window 
	Super+k - focus next window
	Super+h - smaller focused window
	Super+l - larger focused window
	Super+q - close window
	Super+t - tiling layout
	Super+f - floating layout
	Super+m - monocle layout
	Super+Shift+Space - toggle floating
	Super+comma - switch focus to the screen on the left
	Super+period - switch focus to the screen on the right
	Super+Shift+comma - move window to the screen on the left
	Super+Shift+period - move window to the screen on the right
	Super+minus - smaller gaps
	Super+plus - larger gaps
	Super+F10 - reload xrdb
	Super+{1-9} - switch to tag
	Super+0 - show all tags
